    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Painters who create images or decoration on the front or reverse of glass pieces or sheets. Examples are stained glass artists who paint images on the glass, especially the smaller details, such as faces of figures, on windows and panels. To refer to craftsmen who stain glass, use "glass stainers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000076074/Harries and Hicks, Discovering Stained Glass (1996)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000076068/Honour and Fleming, World History of Art (2005)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generalmente, pintores que crean imágenes o decoración en el anverso o reverso de piezas o láminas de vidrio. Se refiere particularmente a artistas de vidrio de color que pintan imágenes en las copas, especialmente los pequeños detalles en ventanas y paneles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In algemene zin, schilders die afbeeldingen of decoraties aanbrengen op de voor- of achterzijde van glazen objecten of glasplaten. Verwijst met name naar de kunstenaars die gebrandschilderd glas maakten, in het bijzonder de fijne details op vensters en vensterpanelen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
